<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 08:09:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列官员告诉国土报，世界法院不太可能在加沙种族灭绝听证会上下令停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/intl-court-of-justice-unlikely-to-order-gaza-cease-fire-israeli-officials-say/0000018c-f711-d432-a7ae-fff9faed0000</link><description>周四和周五的法庭听证会将讨论在加沙目前的情况下是否有可能实施种族灭绝。南非将辩称，根据议会成员和内阁部长的大量声明，以色列有意实施此类行为。因此，南非正在寻求立即颁布临时命令（即所谓的临时措施），以便在实际实施种族灭绝之前在加沙停火并采取其他一些措施</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 06:13:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/intl-court-of-justice-unlikely-to-order-gaza-cease-fire-israeli-officials-say/0000018c-f711-d432-a7ae-fff9faed0000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的共和党对手在爱荷华州辩论中就以色列和反犹太主义问题发生争执</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/trumps-republican-rivals-spar-over-israel-antisemitism-at-iowa-debate/0000018c-f6a6-d432-a7ae-ffff81650000</link><description>美国前驻联合国特使妮基·哈利 (Nikki Haley) 抨击佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯 (Ron DeSantis) 未能充分打击家乡的新纳粹游行和反犹太主义，而德桑蒂斯则指责总统。拜登称美军在中东“任人宰割”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 04:05:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/trumps-republican-rivals-spar-over-israel-antisemitism-at-iowa-debate/0000018c-f6a6-d432-a7ae-ffff81650000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员告诉国土报，世界法院不太可能在加沙种族灭绝听证会上下令停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-present-genocide-case-against-israel-at-world-court-on-thursday/0000018c-f4f8-d3a7-afdf-f5fab49c0000</link><description>预计以色列将于周五在海牙国际法院对指控提出反驳</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 04:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-present-genocide-case-against-israel-at-world-court-on-thursday/0000018c-f4f8-d3a7-afdf-f5fab49c0000</guid></item><item><title>美国希望建立一个“新巴勒斯坦权力机构”来统治加沙。作为交换，阿巴斯希望建国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-wants-a-new-palestinian-authority-to-rule-gaza-in-exchange-abbas-wants-statehood/0000018c-f527-d365-a3ce-f5f7702d0000</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯支持巴勒斯坦总统马哈茂德·阿巴斯建立巴勒斯坦国的步骤，但华盛顿说服以色列做出让步并不容易，这个问题可能会使其与内塔尼亚胡政府发生冲突</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 04:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-wants-a-new-palestinian-authority-to-rule-gaza-in-exchange-abbas-wants-statehood/0000018c-f527-d365-a3ce-f5f7702d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列挫败伊斯兰国支持者在东耶路撒冷的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/ahead-of-world-court-hearing-netanyahu-rejects-calls-for-gaza-population-transfer/0000018c-f676-dd68-a3cf-f6feba5b0000</link><description>以色列总理谴责盟友在海牙种族灭绝听证会当晚发表的言论 ■ 以色列战争内阁在卡塔尔斡旋人质交易的报道中召开会议 ■ 国际法院将于周四在海牙举行种族灭绝听证会 ■ 以色列国防军发现法医证据表明哈马斯在新的基地扣押人质汗尤尼斯地下隧道被发现 ■ 四名巴勒斯坦红新月会员工，两名平民在救护车袭击中丧生 ■ 以色列国防军公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵的名字 ■ 布林肯和阿巴斯在拉马拉讨论巴勒斯坦权力机构改革</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 03:21:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/ahead-of-world-court-hearing-netanyahu-rejects-calls-for-gaza-population-transfer/0000018c-f676-dd68-a3cf-f6feba5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方以潜在暴力为由取消了特拉维夫犹太-阿拉伯和平抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/citing-potential-violence-police-nix-jewish-arab-peace-protest-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f5f6-d432-a7ae-fffffcd40000</link><description>计划在“只有和平才能带来安全”的旗帜下集会的组织者发誓要向最高法院的裁决提出上诉</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 00:46:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/citing-potential-violence-police-nix-jewish-arab-peace-protest-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f5f6-d432-a7ae-fffffcd40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列未成年人因间谍罪入狱 18 个月。调查显示他是以色列国防军情报人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minor-held-for-18-months-for-espionage-before-idf-admitted-controlling-him/0000018c-f4f8-dd68-a3cf-f6fed5530000</link><description>这名当时 17 岁的年轻人被指控发布高度敏感信息，但警方未能按照军方官员的要求彻底调查他的说法。此后经军事情报部门核实，但未告知检方</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 00:04:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minor-held-for-18-months-for-espionage-before-idf-admitted-controlling-him/0000018c-f4f8-dd68-a3cf-f6fed5530000</guid></item><item><title>联合国安理会批准决议要求也门胡塞武装立即停止袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/un-security-council-approves-resolution-demanding-yemens-houthis-immediately-end-attacks/0000018c-f5a5-dd68-a3cf-f7af8a5e0000</link><description>安理会还呼吁胡塞武装释放银河领袖号，这是一艘由日本运营的车辆运输公司，与该组织上个月征用的一名以色列商人有联系</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 23:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/un-security-council-approves-resolution-demanding-yemens-houthis-immediately-end-attacks/0000018c-f5a5-dd68-a3cf-f7af8a5e0000</guid></item><item><title>50 名大屠杀研究人员要求大屠杀纪念馆谴责以色列呼吁在加沙进行种族灭绝的公开言论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/holocaust-researchers-to-yad-vashem-condemn-israeli-public-discourse-calling-for-genocide/0000018c-f53b-dd68-a3cf-f7bf04d20000</link><description>研究人员表示，以色列官员和人士所说的“煽动灭绝”“可能达到种族灭绝的阶段”。他们呼吁大屠杀纪念馆吸取大屠杀的教训</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 21:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/holocaust-researchers-to-yad-vashem-condemn-israeli-public-discourse-calling-for-genocide/0000018c-f53b-dd68-a3cf-f7bf04d20000</guid></item><item><title>专家如何看待国际法院的以色列加沙种族灭绝案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/how-experts-see-israels-gaza-genocide-case-in-the-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-f4f3-d365-a3ce-f5f740260000</link><description>“种族灭绝是一个非常高的门槛。一名专家表示，这不足以证明你集体杀人。以色列必须证明其意图是消灭哈马斯而不是巴勒斯坦人民，并且其大声喧哗的立法者可能会说种族灭绝，但没有实际权力这样做</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 21:29:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/how-experts-see-israels-gaza-genocide-case-in-the-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-f4f3-d365-a3ce-f5f740260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列福利官员称政府预算削减将伤害大屠杀幸存者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-welfare-officials-say-govt-budget-cut-would-harm-massacre-survivors/0000018c-f4f8-dd68-a3cf-f6fee44a0000</link><description>福利部消息人士担心预算削减将达到约 8%，称这对援助撤离人员和弱势群体来说是“致命一击”。阿拉伯当局领导人警告说，估计的削减将严重影响降低犯罪率的努力</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 21:22:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-welfare-officials-say-govt-budget-cut-would-harm-massacre-survivors/0000018c-f4f8-dd68-a3cf-f6fee44a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列公务员的个人信息从政府数据库泄露并被外国实体掌握</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/info-of-israeli-civil-servants-leaked-from-government-database-held-by-foreign-entity/0000018c-f47a-d3a7-afdf-f5fac2000000</link><description>应国家检察官办公室的要求，表面上出于调查该事件的目的，发布了一项禁止媒体报道泄密事件的禁言令。然而，一位专家告诉《国土报》，此类禁言令“主要源于羞耻感，以掩盖他们的失败”</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 18:46:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/info-of-israeli-civil-servants-leaked-from-government-database-held-by-foreign-entity/0000018c-f47a-d3a7-afdf-f5fac2000000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列，政客只有在支持的情况下才可以谈论种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-10/ty-article/.highlight/in-israel-politicians-are-allowed-to-talk-about-genocide-only-if-they-support-it/0000018c-f48c-d365-a3ce-f5fef7ce0000</link><description>七十名议员签署了一项动议，驱逐左翼议员奥弗·卡西夫，因为他支持南非针对以色列的种族灭绝案。与此同时，高级部长的声明正在积极破坏以色列的战争努力</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 18:40:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-10/ty-article/.highlight/in-israel-politicians-are-allowed-to-talk-about-genocide-only-if-they-support-it/0000018c-f48c-d365-a3ce-f5fef7ce0000</guid></item><item><title>战争期间，以色列对巴勒斯坦东耶路撒冷房屋的拆除激增；内盖夫推土工作重新启动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/demolitions-of-palestinian-east-jerusalem-homes-spike-amid-war-negev-bulldozing-renewed/0000018c-f35e-d28a-a1fe-f7fedf170000</link><description>在之前的加沙战争中，当局没有在东耶路撒冷进行拆除活动，以缓解紧张局势。然而，自 10 月份以来，拆毁房屋的速度有所加快，据报告，2023 年被拆除的房屋数量激增了 60%。周三也标志着自战争开始以来，未被承认的贝都因村庄首次被拆除</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 18:24:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/demolitions-of-palestinian-east-jerusalem-homes-spike-amid-war-negev-bulldozing-renewed/0000018c-f35e-d28a-a1fe-f7fedf170000</guid></item><item><title>《华盛顿邮报》调查发现以色列定居者在约旦河西岸枪杀巴勒斯坦青少年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/washington-post-investigation-finds-settlers-shot-and-killed-palestinian-teen-in-west-bank/0000018c-f425-d509-a9ef-f675386e0000</link><description>该报的调查基于“战争开始以来定居者最致命的袭击”的文件和证词，调查显示，一名 17 岁男孩被以色列定居者从背部开枪射击，很可能是在逃跑时</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 17:29:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/washington-post-investigation-finds-settlers-shot-and-killed-palestinian-teen-in-west-bank/0000018c-f425-d509-a9ef-f675386e0000</guid></item><item><title>针对以色列的加沙种族灭绝案：国际法院面临的关键法律问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/gaza-genocide-case-against-israel-the-questions-the-international-court-of-justice-faces/0000018c-f3b7-d6ce-abcc-fbbfe7680000</link><description>南非针对以色列的案件并不是第一次要求世界法院对潜在的种族灭绝做出裁决。先前的决定将给巴勒斯坦人和以色列带来希望，但最终可能会凸显国际法的局限性</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 17:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/gaza-genocide-case-against-israel-the-questions-the-international-court-of-justice-faces/0000018c-f3b7-d6ce-abcc-fbbfe7680000</guid></item><item><title>这位以色列模特正在揭露她作为犹太恐怖分子的女儿的秘密过去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/this-israeli-model-is-revealing-her-secret-past-as-the-daughter-of-a-jewish-terrorist/0000018c-f3c3-d467-afaf-f7cbafd00000</link><description>克拉拉·泰特尔（Clara Teitel）描述了警察在家里逮捕她父亲的那一刻；出生于美国的以色列人，拥有一系列针对巴勒斯坦人和犹太人的未遂恐怖袭击和成功恐怖袭击清单</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 16:38:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/this-israeli-model-is-revealing-her-secret-past-as-the-daughter-of-a-jewish-terrorist/0000018c-f3c3-d467-afaf-f7cbafd00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名在加沙地带中部战斗中丧生的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-central-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018c-f3cf-d6ce-abcc-fbcf43720000</link><description>据以色列国防军称，自10月7日对哈马斯的战争开始以来，已有520名以色列士兵被杀</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 16:21:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-central-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018c-f3cf-d6ce-abcc-fbcf43720000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和南非在联合国最高法院种族灭绝案审理前夕互相吐槽</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/israel-and-south-africa-trade-barbs-on-eve-of-genocide-case-at-uns-top-court/0000018c-f3c2-da04-a7df-f3c7b33c0000</link><description>在为期两天的充满政治色彩的听证会上，国际法院将权衡南非关于种族灭绝的指控；以色列政府发言人称请愿书是“血腥诽谤”</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 15:35:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/israel-and-south-africa-trade-barbs-on-eve-of-genocide-case-at-uns-top-court/0000018c-f3c2-da04-a7df-f3c7b33c0000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯或伊朗是席卷以色列社交媒体的外国运动的幕后黑手，目的是散布内部分裂吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/are-russia-or-iran-behind-campaign-sweeping-israeli-social-media-to-sow-internal-division/0000018c-f363-d431-a7df-fffbf8910000</link><description>过去几周，以色列发起了一场大规模运动，打击士气并散布分歧。一些证据表明俄罗斯人或伊朗人——或者也许两者都是罪魁祸首</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 15:24:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/are-russia-or-iran-behind-campaign-sweeping-israeli-social-media-to-sow-internal-division/0000018c-f363-d431-a7df-fffbf8910000</guid></item></channel></rss>